Package com.elbukkit.plugins.crowd.rules

Class Summary
MaxRule Set maximum number of a creature type
MovementLocationRule Control where entities can be, i.e. entity zones.
Rule Base rule class, basic methods required for checking
SpawnEnvironmentRule A rule that allows or disallows creatures based on the environment, Normal, Nether, (Soon) Ather
SpawnHeightRule A rule that controls spawning based on height.
SpawnLightRule A rule that controls spawning based on light levels.
SpawnLocationRule A rule that prevents creatures from spawning in certain 3D cubes.
SpawnMaterialRule A rule that controls spawning based on the material it spawns on.
SpawnReplaceRule A rule that replaces a creature type with another
SpawnTimeRule A rule to control the time of creature spawning
TargetPlayerRule A rule that prevents creatures from targeting certain players.
